@startuml

actor Usuario
participant Browser
participant Backend
participant "GitHub API" as GitHubAPI
participant OauthService

Usuario -> Backend: GET /oauth2/authorization/github
Backend --> Browser: 302 redirect para página de login GitHub
Browser -> GitHubAPI: Redireciona para GitHub login
Usuario -> GitHubAPI: Autoriza o Planora no GitHub
GitHubAPI -> Backend: code de autorização (callback)
Backend -> GitHubAPI: POST /login/oauth/access_token (code)
GitHubAPI --> Backend: access_token do GitHub
Backend -> OauthService: save(oAuth2User, githubToken)
OauthService --> Backend: LoginResponse (userId, jwtString)
Backend --> Browser: 302 redirect http://localhost:3000/callback/{jwt}
Browser --> Usuario: Armazena JWT em cookie, redireciona para home

@enduml